# This project operates 100% locally and via the Antigravity MCP server.
# No API keys or environment variables are required to run Scout AI.

# Anakin API is accessed natively through the connected Antigravity MCP.
# No ANAKIN_API_KEY is required.

# Supabase / Authentication is currently stubbed/local.
# No SUPABASE keys are required.

# LLMs (Gemini, OpenAI, Anthropic) are not used directly by the frontend.
# No LLM keys are required.
